FIND YOUR STREET'S CLEANING SCHEDULE
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    A new online interactive tool has been launched to help local
    people find out when their streets should be cleaned. The borough's
    street cleansing contract is outsourced to an external provider,
    Continental Landscapes and, following feedback, the Council has
    been discussing with the company how to keep residents
    better informed.

