ANNUAL VOTER REGISTRATION COMMENCES
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    All households in Richmond upon Thames have been sent a form asking
    them to check that the information held on the electoral register
    about those living at that address is correct. This is part of the
    Council's annual voter registration canvass and aims to make sure
    the electoral register is as up-to-date and accurate as possible.

