ROMAN STATUE RETURNS TO STRAWBERRY HILL HOUSE
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    A planned exhibition at Strawberry Hill House to bring back
    important masterpieces will include a 1st Century Roman Imperial
    Eagle, on loan from Gosford House in Scotland after the Strawberry
    Hill Trust received a 5,000 pound grant from the Council.

